productReviews.reviewText: My ant loves to play with it.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
heard about this on new jersey hip hop radio, decided to give it a try.
I saw one of these in Canada and I bought one.
My neighbor Lori has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks whopping.
